data.description: Nothing to do but move right in!  Enjoy single story living with 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths located on a quiet street in Cardington. The open concept kitchen features SS appliances, tile backsplash and an abundance of cabinet space. The flow from the kitchen into the living room and eating area is perfect for cooking meals, entertaining guests and family gatherings. Fresh paint and newer, consistent flooring throughout the living area make this home a true turnkey! The master bedroom is spacious featuring an en suite for added convenience. The outdoor area features a 2 car garage as well as a wooden deck, fitting for relaxing and enjoying the peaceful, private wooded view.  Windows, HVAC and roof all updated in 2019. This home is waiting for you!
